short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copart/IAAI sites action recorder and account manager

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: These tools help dealers buy cars from copart.com and Iaai.com using the company account. The tools also assist in recognizing which user is using this account to purchase cars. Additionally, each user has their personal bids and watchlist.
